        "timestamp": "2018-08-16 02:11:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Hi bin, It's  uncomfortable  to review the content.\n > I recommend  swagger-editor tool to document API that is  more\n > human readable.\n > please refer:  https://swagger.io/tools/swagger-editor\n\nWhat do you mean by \"swagger\" here? I believe swagger is the format for swagger API response, but for design spec , it is always rst.\nI suggest you copy the rst to the online editor for reviewing. http://rst.ninjs.org/",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
