        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> (68 comments)\n\nYes, the format is not perfect,  but this is not a design spec, it is kind of API documentation, so I would prefer defer the fine tuning of format after M4, so it is not hurry to merge it. If you want to take a look at the content right now, here is the online editor for your reference: http://rst.ninjs.org/",
